<h3>Payment Settings</h3>

<p style="margin:20px 0">We're currently researching & experimenting with different payment providers. At the moment we only offer paypal. If you have a strong preference for other providers, <a href="mailto:team@airpair.com">let us know</a>.</p>

<p>Our payout policy is to pay on completion of the chunks you've been booked. I.e. if you're booked for a single 1 hour call - we will pay you straight after the call. If you've been booked for a 5 hour package, we will pay you on completion of your 5 hours. Paying you in blocks minimizes the payment collection fees you pay to the payment providers. It also reduces our administration overhead.</p>

